{
  "attrs": {
    "abstract": "This dataset provides a Climate Data Record of Sea Ice Thickness for the Northern Hemisphere polar region, derived from the SRAL (Synthetic aperture Radar Altimeter) instrument on the Sentinel -3A satellite. This product was generated in the context of the ESA Climate Change Initiative Programme (ESA CCI) by the Sea Ice CCI (Sea_Ice_cci) project.\n\nIt provides monthly sea ice thickness data for the winter months of October to March annually on the satellite measurement grid (Level 3C) at the full sensor resolution for the period October 2016 to April 2024.",
    "catalog_url": "https://catalogue.ceda.ac.uk/uuid/87623591b26042a2aa1bac231f657923",
    "cci_project": "SEAICE",
    "comment": "Northern hemisphere sea ice thickness coverage is limited to the winter month between October and April due to negative effect of surface melt on the retrieval of freeboard. Please consult the Product User Guide (PUG) for more information.",
    "data_type": "SITHICK",
    "ecv": "SEAICE",
    "history": "20250613T150810Z - Product generated with pysiral version 0.11, 2025-10-15T15:56:47.395284 - Fixed error in global attributes",
    "institute": "Alfred-Wegener-Institut Helmholtz-Zentrum f\u00fcr Polar- und Meeresforschung",
    "platform_id": "Sentinel-3A",
    "processing_level": "L3C",
    "product_string": "NH25KMEASE2",
    "product_version": "4-0",
    "project": "Climate Change Initiative - European Space Agency",
    "publication_date": "2025-11-20T12:16:36",
    "references": "CCI+ Sea Ice ECV - Sea Ice Thickness Algorithm Theoretical Basis Document (ATBD) v2.0; CCI+ Sea Ice ECV - Sea Ice Thickness Product User Guide (PUG) v2.0",
    "sensor_id": "SRAL",
    "source": "Altimetry: sentinel3a, Snow depth: Warren Climatology with 50% reduction for first-year sea ice, Mean Sea Surface: DTU21 global mean sea surface, Sea ice Concentration: unknown, Sea ice type:  ESA-SICCI multiyear ice area fraction from daily gridded NSIDC SSMI-SSMIS brightness temperatures version 4 using the NASA-Team algorithm",
    "title": "ESA Sea Ice Climate Change Initiative (Sea_Ice_cci): Northern hemisphere sea ice thickness from Sentinel-3A on a monthly grid (L3C), v4.0",
    "uuid": "87623591b26042a2aa1bac231f657923"
